   <body>
      <p>Direct typing option enables you to search and add products by direct typing.</p>
      <p>To add products by direct typing, please follow the below steps:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Go to the Qualifications &amp; Benefits page.</li>
         <li>Enter the name of the product, which you want to add, in the Product/Category row in the Product Name column. Please view the below images.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432760.jpg"/>
            </fig>
            <fig>
               <image height="102"
                      placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432759.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Enter the required values to the corresponding fields for the added products.</li>
         <li>Click Save.<p>The selected products are added.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
